The evidence with the title 'Obamacare robs medicare of $716 billion to Fund Itself ' says Aug 1, 2012  ... Last week, a new Congressional Budget Office (CBO) report updated the amount of money Obamacare robs out of Medicare from $500 billion to a whopping $716  ... With a raid on Medicare of this magnitude, president Obama's assertion that his new law is protecting seniors and Medicare is astonishing. 
